"```sql\nSELECT posts.Id, posts.ViewCount\nFROM postLinks\nJOIN posts ON postLinks.PostId = posts.Id\nWHERE postLinks.RelatedPostId = 61217;\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the IDs and view counts of all posts that are related to the post with ID 61217, which helps determine the popularity of these related posts. The `postLinks` table is used to find related posts, and the `posts` table provides the view count for each post."